    "title": "Assignment 1",
    "section": "Question 1:",
    "text": "Question 1:\nWhat is the main purpose of subtracting k*view count from the recommended ranking score in a dynamic scoring policy?\nAnswer: This formula reduces the score of product that have been seen too many times so the same items do not always show up at the top. This way, products that have been viewed less get a chance to appear which leads to a more varied and balanced set of recommendations.",
    "crumbs": [
      "Assignment 1"
    ]
