    "section": "Question 2:",
    "text": "Question 2:\nWhat is the term used to describe the pattern where data consumption varies depending on the time of day such as being higher in the evening and lower at night?\nA) Trend\nB) Seasonality\nC) Noise\nD) Outlier\nE) Stationarity",
    "crumbs": [
      "Assignment 1"
